            "title": "中國儒意發23.41億元5年期換股債 年息3.95%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國儒意(00136)今早公布，發行23.41億元將於2030年到期的換股債，年息3.95%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上述債券換股價2.704元，較昨天收市價2.31元有溢價17.06%。集資所得淨額1約23.04億元，約90%用作業務增長及擴展，包括但不限於內容製作、購買劇本及版權、購買電影及電視節目版權；餘下10%用作一般營運資金用途。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14855202-%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e5%84%92%e6%84%8f%e7%99%bc23-41%e5%84%84%e5%85%835%e5%b9%b4%e6%9c%9f%e6%8f%9b%e8%82%a1%e5%82%b5-%e5%b9%b4%e6%81%af3-95",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250114_FI_source-web_00136.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-15 08:55:36",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "華潤置地上月合同銷售按年降13.3% 首季則升0.9% 首季經常性收入增10.6%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">華潤置地(01109)公布，今年3月份實現總合同銷售約261億元(人民幣．下同)，涉及樓面90.6萬平方米，按年分別降13.3%及27.9%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：華潤置地官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250224_FI_source-web_01109.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：華潤置地官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250224_FI_source-web_01109.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：華潤置地官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">若將今年首3個月合計，集團累計合同銷售約512億元，按年升0.9%；涉及樓面197.9萬平方米，按年減少11.8%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">在經常性收入方面，華潤置地於今年3月份的收入約40億元，按年增長8.5%；其中經營性不動產業務租金收入約25.7億元，按年升12.3%。今年首季累計經常性收入約123.9億元，按年升10.6%，其中經營性不動產業務租金收入80.3億元，按年增長12.6%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14855188-%e8%8f%af%e6%bd%a4%e7%bd%ae%e5%9c%b0%e4%b8%8a%e6%9c%88%e5%90%88%e5%90%8c%e9%8a%b7%e5%94%ae%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e9%99%8d13-3-%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e5%89%87%e5%8d%870-9-%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e7%b6%93%e5%b8%b8",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250317_FI_source-web_01109.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-15 08:45:43",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
